        <p>Comprehensive financial planning services to help you achieve your personal and business financial goals.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Retirement planning</li>
          <li>Investment strategies</li>
          <li>Estate planning</li>
          <li>Risk management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="10" y="20" width="40" height="25" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="3"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="32" r="5" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
