          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Audit Support</h3>
        <p>Professional audit support and representation to ensure compliance and resolve any issues with tax authorities.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>IRS audit representation</li>
          <li>State audit support</li>
          <li>Document preparation</li>
          <li>Compliance reviews</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="10" y="10" width="40" height="40" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" rx="4"/>
            <path d="M20 25 L25 30 L40 15" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="35" x2="40" y2="35" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="40" x2="35" y2="40" stroke="var(--color-sage)" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Compliance Services</h3>
        <p>Stay compliant with ever-changing regulations and requirements with our comprehensive compliance services.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Regulatory compliance</li>
          <li>Filing requirements</li>
          <li>Record keeping</li>
          <li>Policy development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sage) 0%, var(--color-sage-dark) 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .services-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .services-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .service-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .service-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-features li::before {
    content: 'âœ“';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-sage);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .services-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>